==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unconverted
<hw>Un`con*vert"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
converted or exchanged.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not changed in opinion, or from one faith to
another.</def> Specifically: --⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sd>(a)</sd> <def>Not persuaded of the truth of the Christian
religion; heathenish.</def> <rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sd>(b)</sd> <def>Unregenerate; sinful; impenitent.</def>
<rj><au>Baxter.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncord</ent>⟦br⟧
